&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>安装依赖&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;code>$ sudo apt install build-essential flex bison dwarves libssl-dev libelf-dev&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
